# RUR-PLE-korean-project ##The RURPLE Korean project was interrupted in 2014. The project is designed to receive education in the Samsung "Junior Software Academy".
In fact, this program is discontinued in 2012, but ... I wanted to use more progress has been localized.
It is now operating in the web. http://reeborg.ca
##Python Version
Source modification has been working with Python 2.5.4
